name: Supernova
description:
The third and final piece in the Milky Way series. The end of our Suns life characterised by a Supernova event will push humans in search of other habitable systems.  We will be leaving the local system in the next series to explore other interesting and unique collections of planets, systems and never before seen spacial objects which will blow your mind. 

As you now know I arrived from the Galaxy GN-z11 to visit planet “Earth” . My main goal is to expand the humans mind and awareness on what can be found and experienced from Earth to my home galaxy. 

Generated using R code which is intended for use in statistical analysis. Package by KoenDerks
